Items:
a. Having all of the following characteristics:
1C118.a
Containing 17.0-23.0 weight percent chromium and 4.5-7.0 weight percent nickel;
a.1. Containing 17.0-23.0 weight percent chromium and 4.5-7.0 weight percent nickel;
Having a titanium content of greater than 0.10 weight percent; and
a.2. Having a titanium content of greater than 0.10 weight percent; and
A ferritic-austenitic microstructure (also referred to as a two-phase microstructure) of which at least 10 percent is austenite by volume (according to ASTM E-1181-87 or national equivalents), and
a.3. A ferritic-austenitic microstructure (also referred to as a two-phase microstructure) of which at least 10 percent is austenite by volume (according to ASTM E-1181-87 or national equivalents), and
Having any of the following forms:
b. Having any of the following forms:
Ingots or bars having a size of 100 mm or more in each dimension;
b.1. Ingots or bars having a size of 100 mm or more in each dimension;
Sheets having a width of 600 mm or more and a thickness of 3 mm or less; or
b.2. Sheets having a width of 600 mm or more and a thickness of 3 mm or less; or
Tubes having an outer diameter of 600 mm or more and a wall thickness of 3 mm or less.
b.3. Tubes having an outer diameter of 600 mm or more and a wall thickness of 3 mm or less.
